     <div type="encomium">
   <pb facs="9"/>
   <head>In laudem operis.</head>
   <l>WOrds are the pensils, whereby drawne we sinde</l>
   <l>The picture of the inward man, the minde.</l>
   <l>Such thoughts, such words; such words, such is the man.</l>
   <l>Say; is this Spirit a Plebey<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>an?</l>
   <l>That like the singing Larke doth mount so high,</l>
   <l>We cannot reach them with an earthly eye.</l>
   <closer>
      <signed>W.P.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
